Multi-Support Template Library

Collaboration diagram for Multi-Support Template Library:

Detailed Description

This library is a separable part of the Rose project.

This library supports many things related to Abstract Syntax Trees. Currently the library is somewhat dependent upon Rose, but this will be fixed.
